     5	
     6	/**
     7	 * Feature Opt-In Effective State Computation
     8	 * ==========================================
     9	 *
    10	 * This module computes whether a feature is effectively enabled for a user
    11	 * based on global, organization, team, and user-level settings.
    12	 *
    13	 * Two policies are supported:
    14	 * - `permissive` (default): User opt-in can activate the feature; disables only win if ALL teams disable
    15	 * - `strict`: User opt-in alone is NOT enough; requires explicit enable from org/team; ANY disable blocks
    16	 *
    17	 *
    18	 * SCENARIO TABLE - PERMISSIVE POLICY
    19	 * ============================================
    20	 *
    21	 * | # | Global | Org      | Teams                    | User     | Result  | Reason                        |
    22	 * |---|--------|----------|--------------------------|----------|---------|-------------------------------|
    23	 * | 1 | true   | inherit  | [inherit, inherit]       | enabled  | ALLOWED | User opt-in activates         |
    24	 * | 2 | true   | inherit  | [enabled, inherit]       | inherit  | ALLOWED | Team enablement propagates    |
    25	 * | 3 | true   | inherit  | [inherit, inherit]       | inherit  | BLOCKED | No explicit enablement        |
    26	 * | 4 | true   | inherit  | [enabled, disabled]      | inherit  | ALLOWED | At least one team enabled     |
    27	 * | 5 | true   | enabled  | [inherit]                | inherit  | ALLOWED | Org enablement propagates     |
    28	 * | 6 | true   | enabled  | [disabled, disabled]     | enabled  | BLOCKED | All teams disabled            |
    29	 * | 7 | true   | disabled | [enabled]                | enabled  | BLOCKED | Org disabled blocks all       |
    30	 * | 8 | true   | inherit  | [disabled]               | enabled  | BLOCKED | All teams disabled            |
    31	 * | 9 | true   | inherit  | [enabled]                | disabled | BLOCKED | User disabled                 |
    32	 * |10 | false  | enabled  | [enabled]                | enabled  | BLOCKED | Global disabled               |
    33	 *
    34	 *
    35	 * SCENARIO TABLE - STRICT POLICY
    36	 * ==============================
    37	 *
    38	 * | # | Global | Org      | Teams                    | User     | Result  | Reason                        |
    39	 * |---|--------|----------|--------------------------|----------|---------|-------------------------------|
    40	 * | 1 | true   | inherit  | [inherit, inherit]       | inherit  | BLOCKED | No explicit enablement        |
    41	 * | 2 | true   | inherit  | [inherit, inherit]       | enabled  | BLOCKED | User-only not allowed         |
    42	 * | 3 | true   | inherit  | [enabled, inherit]       | inherit  | ALLOWED | Team enablement works         |
    43	 * | 4 | true   | inherit  | [enabled, inherit]       | enabled  | ALLOWED | Team + user enabled           |
